[🚇 #StormscapeStayHome]
4 LAYERS STRAWBERRY MATCHA MILK?!
Because I have leftover strawberries and matcha from the Strawberry Matcha Toast I made previously, decided to make a drink out of it!
.
Steps
1️⃣ Add boba (optional) into empty glass
2️⃣ Cook FROZEN strawberry: Sugar in the ratio of 3:1 to get the semi-liquid strawberry compote
3️⃣ Add 2 ice cream scoops worth of Strawberry compote onto the boba 
4️⃣ Add in Fresh Milk until 80% full
5️⃣ Whisk your matcha to yield 40ml and pour into 4️⃣
.
